title: Yoast SEO v2.2.2 - Premium WordPress Plugins
description:
WordPress on its own is relatively easy to optimize, but its SEO functionality should be extended using WordPress plugins. Yoast offers several WordPress plugins to optimize your WordPress SEO, built around one core WordPress SEO plugin. Contains external links.

To install:

1. Upload to plugin directory in wordpress
2. Activate through plugin menu in wp-admin
